ces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n德國佬直頭閘都無<br />\n自覺買飛啦<br />\n<br />\n人種係有高低之分既<br />\n不得不承認</blockquote><br />\n你點睇輕鐵？</blockquote><br />\n住得屯天元就已經係高質保證啦，日日涯兩三粒鐘車程返工都無怨過，冬天凍兩度都未撚驚<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係市區人可以答西鐵入黎，計我話錦上路之前既車站都應該全部拆闡"},{"pid":"5eba8f2103fee4bc67c3e4e75dceb5e7981f47ff","tid":500970,"uid":158504,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:15:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好慘<br />\n諗住屌全世界都唔鍾意既地鐵攞認同<br />\n點知搞成咁</blockquote><br />\n佢跟本係井底之蛙未撚見過世面<br />\n樓主去紐約地鐵訓番晚再出番黎先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歐/美地鐵=臭尿味+污糟+老鼠+小偷"},{"pid":"5e295cd824561d2b559a5ec3dd63583d3c622e3a","tid":500970,"uid":114175,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:20:17.000Z","msg":"香港有咁多盲毛依家連八達通都未用得掂, 地鐵一整contactless payment 條龍肯定打哂蛇餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啱啱入閘先比前面個阿嬋磨袋阻住半分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c25c683bb22e02a6206656e5d21fff5b1c3c9a","tid":500970,"uid":74858,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:26:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/232439_8d314392ce2eaa90c3761a613cbff967.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F232439_8d314392ce2eaa90c3761a613cbff967.jpg&h=8ce93f30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵除咗delay  其他算係咁啦<br />\n英國佬貼個牌出黎叫你返工啦咁多嗲咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28702a7d048cca03a312bb9278cd056be94b1240","tid":500970,"uid":42064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:29:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用咁耐都咁新淨<br />\n新嗰d 膠身一陣就又殘又污糟</blockquote><br />\n如果係佢post嗰種，我覺得ok。<br />\n但黃埔嗰種，真係好柒"},{"pid":"a760e83e64702ca1741ed4613bbd0910d05fce02","tid":500970,"uid":19949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:31:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用咁耐都咁新淨<br />\n新嗰d 膠身一陣就又殘又污糟</blockquote><br />\n如果係佢post嗰種，我覺得ok。<br />\n但黃埔嗰種，真係好柒</blockquote><br />\n果種係九鐵引入<br />\n點會好似地鐵噤on9用白色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aca1378d4bdf67df26a7c88dd121004070f875d","tid":500970,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:33:53.000Z","msg":"樓主矮撚比碌棍打到條撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"960a426f0a52a693fa676f498f921dcec71368a1","tid":500970,"uid":45943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:35:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/232439_8d314392ce2eaa90c3761a613cbff967.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F232439_8d314392ce2eaa90c3761a613cbff967.jpg&h=8ce93f30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵除咗delay  其他算係咁啦<br />\n英國佬貼個牌出黎叫你返工啦咁多嗲咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢種黑色幽默係香港又會有一大堆港豬走出黎瓜瓜叫"},{"pid":"57f43b4cb4b43557f3dfb05ef787503c9b3676a7","tid":500970,"uid":158504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:44:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用咁耐都咁新淨<br />\n新嗰d 膠身一陣就又殘又污糟</blockquote><br />\n如果係佢post嗰種，我覺得ok。<br />\n但黃埔嗰種，真係好柒</blockquote><br />\n果種係九鐵引入<br />\n點會好似地鐵噤on9用白色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n九鐵紅藍其實幾靚<br />\n反而地鐵乜Q都油白色銀色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc28a53892124141d534df2cc0e26a29c37eb119","tid":500970,"uid":10894,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:45:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb008f437492ec64c217ad6a777b8f78635fc5ce","tid":500970,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:58:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/232439_8d314392ce2eaa90c3761a613cbff967.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F232439_8d314392ce2eaa90c3761a613cbff967.jpg&h=8ce93f30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵除咗delay  其他算係咁啦<br />\n英國佬貼個牌出黎叫你返工啦咁多嗲咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mPMMmZDcGUg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmPMMmZDcGUg&d=WzhYenQXNUg8a2tZG0UdSACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=aa99bd8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mPMMmZDcGUg</a>"},{"pid":"23841c3fba9db8a354706d1c4e7dfeb8b837a250","tid":500970,"uid":117679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T16:23:49.000Z","msg":"三角棍入閘機，印象中好似係瑞士製造，所以好襟用，而且真係幾難衝到閘。<br />\n而新式嗰啲就係大陸製，聽講係幾易壞。同埋一衝，塊膠板好易撞到入面嘅零件有問題。<br />\n<br />\n同埋點解唔發展MOBILE PAYMENT? 因為八達通嘅大股東係港鐵公司囉。"},{"pid":"0888f8b003a671716820d47321c403b4ede2fb3c","tid":500970,"uid":117679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T16:26:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你咁都無能 ？ 琴日就係靠佢先阻到隻蝗入閘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一年賺咁多錢，阻一個兩個咁又點話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有呢種閘一樣可以沖到閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主...乜咁大陸人諗法....<br />\n<br />\n你不如話港鐵大股東都係香港政府，香港政府啲錢咪又係香港市民。咁點解要我俾錢?"},{"pid":"606787ccee56b8b14adea3286faefed0d5717c4d","tid":500970,"uid":117679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T16:28:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正路唔係用手推咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係用手推.... 唔會用條撚撞碌棍黎推.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a55316e724fcba91ba877d765d0b9072f5f1670","tid":500970,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T16:35:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多個站好耐以前仲有用樓主講嗰隻，跟住唔知點解換翻哂三椂棍嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為逃票問題太嚴重囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別係羅湖"},{"pid":"4cd35c09e903e40edec3896185e4a7a7af4818e9","tid":500970,"uid":26602,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T16:37:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本啲閘開住添   你有比錢唔會阻到你   <br />\n香港質素係點咪比咩質素你</blockquote><br />\n唔係咁講<br />\n香港初期都好似日本咁長開，冇拍卡插飛先閂個閘截住你<br />\n係有班仆街家長投訴夾親小朋友先改到長時間閂埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c63d1901dc20ab8e5a97e91dc4587e026147bcb","tid":500970,"uid":27432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T16:39:26.000Z","msg":"ON9 <br />\n新果隻閘反應慢好多架<br />\n繁忙時間仲會HANG 機<br />\n傻9"},{"pid":"62e32428ae570cb8813462213498ecb2a4de90a3","tid":500970,"uid":51127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T16:39:57.000Z","msg":"其實所有上市公司都會執行資產管理，所有設備在安裝時其實會定明左使用年期，其價值按年減少，到預定年期其價值會等於零。（有關資產資料在年報會有）<br />\n<br />\n如在資產價值未為零前更換，在帳面上會有不按預期的拆舊損失，要向股東解釋。"},{"pid":"818963793a20f585b3926e3707388105774f61c1","tid":500970,"uid":45232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T16:54:03.000Z","msg":"其實舊闡幾好用"},{"pid":"356048a562bfa6303fa7cebea811bfe58aa54d1a","tid":500970,"uid":49634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T17:38:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/232439_8d314392ce2eaa90c3761a613cbff967.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F232439_8d314392ce2eaa90c3761a613cbff967.jpg&h=8ce93f30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵除咗delay  其他算係咁啦<br />\n英國佬貼個牌出黎叫你返工啦咁多嗲咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n倫敦地鐵仲要連電話都收唔到<br />\n約咗朋友遲到都唔知點同人講聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3fc7cc69d7e552e6e8010c75a0df38e8f1bbf7c","tid":500970,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T17:45:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實好心啦<br />\n學下人地日本咁直頭乜都唔完整得個吉閘<br />\n咁真係好肉酸囉<br />\n驚死人走你車錢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國人是要管的<br />\n日本人做到的<br />\n中國人不會做得到</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">#82 bbchu &bull; 1h</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"89a905a57a690849f350d71a58aa655e9490ea48","tid":500970,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T17:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中國中鐵屌打mtr啦  唔同級數</blockquote><br />\n又打呢句，發現打手</blockquote><br />\n港鐵都有人撐你先係打手。成日有事故又唔道歉。放火案無人識用設施。波板糖人on99。公家地趕音樂人走。大把西野都仲有人撐。</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">#45 羅拔利雲度夫斯基 &bull; 4h</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"88592feb83773b5b0a7e65e9178b912a000a1954","tid":500970,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T18:13:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日本啲閘開住添   你有比錢唔會阻到你   <br />\n香港質素係點咪比咩質素你</blockquote><br />\n唔係咁講<br />\n香港初期都好似日本咁長開，冇拍卡插飛先閂個閘截住你<br />\n係有班仆街家長投訴夾親小朋友先改到長時間閂埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過我都有印象以前啲闊閘機好撚惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n閂得又快又大力<br />\n仲試過夾住左我老母個手袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53378379d6150acae03d1a968ff74e9a0f070be1","tid":500970,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T18:35:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實所有上市公司都會執行資產管理，所有設備在安裝時其實會定明左使用年期，其價值按年減少，到預定年期其價值會等於零。（有關資產資料在年報會有）<br />\n<br />\n如在資產價值未為零前更換，在帳面上會有不按預期的拆舊損失，要向股東解釋。</blockquote><br />\n啲閘用咗幾十年晨早過晒折舊期啦阿專家<br />\n廢鐵得閒屎忽痕就換下啲指示牌有冇問過啲股東呀阿專家"},{"pid":"7239a0d9460ac8986d2b7ad4e0bb120af183d488","tid":500970,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T18:44:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實舊闡幾好用</blockquote><br />\n又襟又易打理<br />\n洗鋼水抹下就新嘅一樣<br />\n走去換d 垃圾機<br />\n不過而家香港大勢都係咁<br />\n垃圾換走d 好野<br />\n下次佢仆街又要人換地磚"},{"pid":"507e08b5beae0b7f05d73797fbc8eed443fa0647","tid":500970,"uid":4519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T18:48:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實舊闡幾好用</blockquote><br />\n又襟又易打理<br />\n洗鋼水抹下就新嘅一樣<br />\n走去換d 垃圾機<br />\n不過而家香港大勢都係咁<br />\n垃圾換走d 好野<br />\n下次佢仆街又要人換地磚</blockquote><br />\n地磚換左啦，你唔見好多站已經係白色彷雲石磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dda701c14d781c7ccb622582f4e2ce034ae4a75","tid":500970,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T18:48:31.000Z","msg":"係囉<br />\n<br />\n好撚同意<br />\n<br />\n上次趕時間返工<br />\n<br />\n見到架車就嚟開  一嘢衝埋去個閘<br />\n<br />\n嘟唔到卡  <br />\n<br />\n砰一聲<br />\n<br />\n周圍d乘客都望撚住我<br />\n<br />\n訓起地下到等到我清醒返<br />\n<br />\n原來我碌勁扯得太行  閘機支棍俾我撞到成支彎左<br />\n<br />\n結果賠左成半個月人工<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係咁硬咁粗  撞親淨係上連登出po就唔駛咁煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a22a5c0cd2cfbaa4b69cbe4454959c6f98e063","tid":500970,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T18:51:31.000Z","msg":"成日見D支那人響闊閘機兩個、三個咁入閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}